NAME

DateTime::Locale::teo_KE - Locale data examples for the Teso Kenya (teo-KE) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Teso Kenya locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Nakaare, 5 Omuk 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Nakakany, 22 Opoo 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Nakasabiti, 15 Osokosokoma -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Omuk 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Opoo 1995
